'''khawaarij''' waa urur diimeed soo baxay waagii hore ee islaamka [[Cali bin Abii Daalib|cali bin abii daalib]] ayee ku sameeyeen kacdoon, waxey ka soo horjeesteen wada hadalkii uu la galay [[Mucawiya|mucaawiya]], [[Cali]] ayaa ku laayay [[dagaalkii nahrawaan]] sanadkii 38H, laakin sanadkii 40aad ee hijriga shirqool ay maleegeen ayee ku dileen cali oo masjidka galaaya.
